# Style Forage: Design System & Style Guide

A guide to the visual language and user experience principles of Style Forage.

## Tailwind v4 Configuration

Custom theme values are defined in `index.css` using `@theme` blocks. When adding new design tokens:

```css
@theme {
  --color-custom-name: #hexvalue;
  --font-custom: 'Font Name', fallback;
}
```

